                     <interp inst="t18470816-1760-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 67 yards of sheet<lb></lb>ing, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18470816-name-294" type="victimName">
